生蠔(steak house個間)"},{"pid":"ea0065c25a080e927ddec67f1004a6846123e230","tid":395820,"uid":58791,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:08:18.000Z","msg":"食自助餐真係好難回本，以前就話勁食生蠔就回本，但係而家出去買都係10鬆d一隻，人地一大批拎我諗4-5蚊隻就得，而家要400蚊以上既自助餐先有蠔，你都要食40幾-50隻先叫做回本，算你食得落咁多蠔你都食唔落其他野，咁點解唔拎400蚊直接買靚蠔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雪波士頓龍蝦仔之前759都係30幾40蚊隻，人地一大批拎我諗20-30蚊搞掂，咁易食到回本開自助餐丫放題丫韓燒丫打邊爐丫就執笠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72c7ee4444cc1e722562e79da725c9fdf2366a6a","tid":395820,"uid":28762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:08:43.000Z","msg":"人地餐廳批發入貨可能圍到10蚊隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc3d427bd760a8a6ee78aecad08320dbc50605c","tid":395820,"uid":77461,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:10:14.000Z","msg":"前幾日經過馬可孛羅，見到好多龍蝦一車車咁送入去，有好多隻流眼淚 佢地知就快俾人殺...真係好慘!<br />\n<br />\n龍蝦係有靈性，幫酒店賺錢....請大家唔好食龍蝦! 我都已經開始戒...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85b5ba55a46f645311334afd23eea660926bd2e5","tid":395820,"uid":19196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:13:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食自助餐真係好難回本，以前就話勁食生蠔就回本，但係而家出去買都係10鬆d一隻，人地一大批拎我諗4-5蚊隻就得，而家要400蚊以上既自助餐先有蠔，你都要食40幾-50隻先叫做回本，算你食得落咁多蠔你都食唔落其他野，咁點解唔拎400蚊直接買靚蠔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雪波士頓龍蝦仔之前759都係30幾40蚊隻，人地一大批拎我諗20-30蚊搞掂，咁易食到回本開自助餐丫放題丫韓燒丫打邊爐丫就執笠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n40-50隻生蠔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n痾到開花"},{"pid":"411efde7b27a5471d7718d5188b8fb543b5094ec","tid":395820,"uid":10971,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:14:30.000Z","msg":"食buffet 貪佢多款食一家人開心下姐<br />\n<br />\n下下諗食乜回本有冇煩d"},{"pid":"40e54374705a9486d88809e7c508bf243b836aa4","tid":395820,"uid":131041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:14:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前幾日經過馬可孛羅，見到好多龍蝦一車車咁送入去，有好多隻流眼淚 佢地知就快俾人殺...真係好慘!<br />\n<br />\n龍蝦係有靈性，幫酒店賺錢....請大家唔好食龍蝦! 我都已經開始戒...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c4446585a66caa79dededde165c7f883595c49","tid":395820,"uid":19196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:15:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食buffet 貪佢多款食一家人開心下姐<br />\n<br />\n下下諗食乜回本有冇煩d</blockquote><br />\n咩都計住，果樣唔食得 果樣唔食得<br />\n<br />\n人生好坎坷"},{"pid":"ebed4634c218bf7eef9d4c586f33c646c0ee0f7c","tid":395820,"uid":15336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:17:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>食自助餐真係好難回本，以前就話勁食生蠔就回本，但係而家出去買都係10鬆d一隻，人地一大批拎我諗4-5蚊隻就得，而家要400蚊以上既自助餐先有蠔，你都要食40幾-50隻先叫做回本，算你食得落咁多蠔你都食唔落其他野，咁點解唔拎400蚊直接買靚蠔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雪波士頓龍蝦仔之前759都係30幾40蚊隻，人地一大批拎我諗20-30蚊搞掂，咁易食到回本開自助餐丫放題丫韓燒丫打邊爐丫就執笠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n40-50隻生蠔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n痾到開花</blockquote><br />\n我人生第一次食生蠔係自助餐食<br />\n果度唔係排隊等佢開<br />\n佢係開晒放晒係盤度<br />\n我果次真係食左三打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3232018fa33133567848c81a42da10b9fedd899","tid":395820,"uid":36968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:18:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有任食象拔蚌嗰啲，如果有人講我聽邊度有得平買麻煩講我聽，我都唔想成日食自助餐</blockquote><br />\nMezza 9 <br />\n不過係澳門 仲要好難訂位"},{"pid":"3b7be6065be7ff0d27a5dce771c8bb298b87aded","tid":395820,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:20:36.000Z","msg":"最睇唔起大魚大肉咁食嘢法<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n貴夾唔飽先係classy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18570b1f4a607b42a681ee1c8868057fbe1a6663","tid":395820,"uid":59720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:20:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自己去街市買新鮮咪百幾蚊斤<br />\n急凍龍蝦酒店叫貨30蚊有隻<br />\n成陣雪味，你食到回本咪食囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新鮮同冰鮮個價差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n尖沙咀唔記得邊間酒店食過，肯定係識郁架喎"},{"pid":"24a1fd37a16c034ec29729b80b567a68efe99605","tid":395820,"uid":66580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:22:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自己去街市買新鮮咪百幾蚊斤<br />\n急凍龍蝦酒店叫貨30蚊有隻<br />\n成陣雪味，你食到回本咪食囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新鮮同冰鮮個價差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n尖沙咀唔記得邊間酒店食過，肯定係識郁架喎</blockquote><br />\n係咪星光大道嗰間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f376bf5a56956550276c988a6987aa887dbe8bc3","tid":395820,"uid":45147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:23:13.000Z","msg":"自助餐根本食氣氛，坐係度吹水同比個機會自己狂食野一次半次姐，又可以睇下人拎乜野食笑鳩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本你比近千蚊食五星都係會失望(只講野食)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99d1ac46cf25c627971601844422c3c90b7e207f","tid":395820,"uid":77330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:31:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自己去街市買新鮮咪百幾蚊斤<br />\n急凍龍蝦酒店叫貨30蚊有隻<br />\n成陣雪味，你食到回本咪食囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新鮮同冰鮮個價差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n尖沙咀唔記得邊間酒店食過，肯定係識郁架喎</blockquote><br />\n係咪星光大道嗰間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nk11 果間？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c9a1f2f6633e3826f25f695b3323c3d56bc160","tid":395820,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:32:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲有任食象拔蚌嗰啲，如果有人講我聽邊度有得平買麻煩講我聽，我都唔想成日食自助餐</blockquote><br />\nMezza 9 <br />\n不過係澳門 仲要好難訂位</blockquote><br />\n我唔想成日食自助餐,所以想問邊度有得買平象拔蚌,唔係問自助餐啊"},{"pid":"cf3800f40037e2a400a5ce26ff06b7ba89c5fce5","tid":395820,"uid":5777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:35:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自己去街市買新鮮咪百幾蚊斤<br />\n急凍龍蝦酒店叫貨30蚊有隻<br />\n成陣雪味，你食到回本咪食囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新鮮同冰鮮個價差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n尖沙咀唔記得邊間酒店食過，肯定係識郁架喎</blockquote><br />\n係咪星光大道嗰間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nk11 果間？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n凱悅 好抵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcbeafaa96888b64c869a41e108764ae4874fdd2","tid":395820,"uid":76247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:36:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食自助餐唔好諗回本，輸硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用自助餐價錢，我寧願出去單點</blockquote><br />\n單點計翻可能仲貴過buffet"},{"pid":"0d7852e447f4c80d5debd0f9f1fa1c3a299272cb","tid":395820,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:41:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">邊度買平象拔蚌同龍蝦???如果夠平嘅話,我以後唔食自助餐!!!!!!!</span>"},{"pid":"666b9d389c2f0e1982aa4888b28bed276edd7267","tid":395820,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:50:41.000Z","msg":"自助餐係會比平時食多啲，但唔係要食返幾舊水返黎囉，人地做生意點都係計過有賺先做，食客身份係去享受，唔係同生意佬對賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c2ad8425ace7b4876e6ebab3dd0477e2e2cf94","tid":395820,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:51:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自助餐係會比平時食多啲，但唔係要食返幾舊水返黎囉，人地做生意點都係計過有賺先做，食客身份係去享受，唔係同生意佬對賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n酒店來貨價係平，但係你自己都搵唔到邊度入貨可以咁平啦，最終咪又要食自助餐"},{"pid":"13c59736ed64a44ac2ba992814b97f1fc20d7ae8","tid":395820,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:52:36.000Z","msg":"打手"},{"pid":"181834684e3ebb297033c7fe1acb75c682566099","tid":395820,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:55:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打手</blockquote><br />\n唔係囉"},{"pid":"8ad335443685b4e44215bdb307cdb66c9e401b74","tid":395820,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:01:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自助餐係會比平時食多啲，但唔係要食返幾舊水返黎囉，人地做生意點都係計過有賺先做，食客身份係去享受，唔係同生意佬對賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n酒店來貨價係平，但係你自己都搵唔到邊度入貨可以咁平啦，最終咪又要食自助餐</blockquote><br />\n關咩事，自己煮好食好多，根本同食自助餐兩回事"},{"pid":"3e35e5e7e15c5dfd48c79832fe1cedd914b77dd2","tid":395820,"uid":39866,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:07:27.000Z","msg":"見你問得呢條問題 就知你唔熟行情<br />\n<br />\n其實做得呢d既酒店都係大財主<br />\n一早已經做好哂對沖 你只要得閒望下<br />\n就會發現附近幾間診所都係同一個老闆<br />\n<br />\n呢d垃圾龍蝦比盡三四十蚊隻<br />\n你要回本最少食20隻<br />\n<br />\n你見強國d柒頭皮連食十隻已經肌肉溶解症<br />\n你食廿隻 唔好話肌肉 連骨都熔撚埋<br />\n你一出門口訓低 <br />\n即時有十幾個醫生準備好幫你開刀<br />\n跟手收返你十皮八皮"},{"pid":"96f6cfd292080b37552cdbfdafb8bf2f89e28630","tid":395820,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:09:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自助餐係會比平時食多啲，但唔係要食返幾舊水返黎囉，人地做生意點都係計過有賺先做，食客身份係去享受，唔係同生意佬對賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n酒店來貨價係平，但係你自己都搵唔到邊度入貨可以咁平啦，最終咪又要食自助餐</blockquote><br />\n關咩事，自己煮好食好多，根本同食自助餐兩回事</blockquote><br />\n咁你講得出邊間買龍蝦同象拔蚌平咩??如果夠平嘅話,我以後唔食自助餐!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"c6202e1a26c57e21930fbe64811ff355543732f8","tid":395820,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:10:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/11/181006_882c821a797b08fadc927da2af346334.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F11%2F181006_882c821a797b08fadc927da2af346334.jpg&h=44d97011&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n龍蝦鮑魚帶子刺身全部任食我都唔知佢點賺<br />\n<br />\n仲有鴨肝片皮鴨HD雪糕"},{"pid":"dac6fb6aa9a24317f36dffc23896ae4a00d57096","tid":395820,"uid":45431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:12:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自助餐係會比平時食多啲，但唔係要食返幾舊水返黎囉，人地做生意點都係計過有賺先做，食客身份係去享受，唔係同生意佬對賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n酒店來貨價係平，但係你自己都搵唔到邊度入貨可以咁平啦，最終咪又要食自助餐</blockquote><br />\n關咩事，自己煮好食好多，根本同食自助餐兩回事</blockquote><br />\n咁你講得出邊間買龍蝦同象拔蚌平咩??如果夠平嘅話,我以後唔食自助餐!!!!!!!</blockquote><br />\n波蝦唔做打手，去google打食材，網上訂購，好多間都平<br />\n象拔蚌大蚌一定貴，平既食細蚌，三十幾蚊隻，唔會差過大蚌。去大啲既街市水檔已經有得賣。"},{"pid":"3f00bc1b79e5acf752d215e56d6367e1fa0d8e2a","tid":395820,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:14:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自助餐係會比平時食多啲，但唔係要食返幾舊水返黎囉，人地做生意點都係計過有賺先做，食客身份係去享受，唔係同生意佬對賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n酒店來貨價係平，但係你自己都搵唔到邊度入貨可以咁平啦，最終咪又要食自助餐</blockquote><br />\n關咩事，自己煮好食好多，根本同食自助餐兩回事</blockquote><br />\n咁你講得出邊間買龍蝦同象拔蚌平咩??如果夠平嘅話,我以後唔食自助餐!!!!!!!</blockquote><br />\n波蝦唔做打手，去google打食材，網上訂購，好多間都平<br />\n象拔蚌大蚌一定貴，平既食細蚌，三十幾蚊隻，唔會差過大蚌。去大啲既街市水檔已經有得賣。</blockquote><br />\n象拔蚌依家都有得任食啦,食十隻已經回本"},{"pid":"040f832851c273b84943244e5a04230668057d41","tid":395820,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:16:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自助餐係會比平時食多啲，但唔係要食返幾舊水返黎囉，人地做生意點都係計過有賺先做，食客身份係去享受，唔係同生意佬對賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n酒店來貨價係平，但係你自己都搵唔到邊度入貨可以咁平啦，最終咪又要食自助餐</blockquote><br />\n關咩事，自己煮好食好多，根本同食自助餐兩回事</blockquote><br />\n咁你講得出邊間買龍蝦同象拔蚌平咩??如果夠平嘅話,我以後唔食自助餐!!!!!!!</blockquote><br />\n波蝦唔做打手，去google打食材，網上訂購，好多間都平<br />\n象拔蚌大蚌一定貴，平既食細蚌，三十幾蚊隻，唔會差過大蚌。去大啲既街市水檔已經有得賣。</blockquote><br />\n象拔蚌依家都有得任食啦,食十隻已經回本</blockquote><br />\n都係嗰句，你無要求成日諗回本咪出去食自助餐。我就寧願享受優質食物，而唔係死食爛食。"},{"pid":"ceb9041265f662150283f8d17417467745f49859","tid":395820,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:19:09.000Z","msg":"我自己就係試過搵過一係無,一係就貴到抽筋,最終都係去咗食自助餐,如果有得平我都唔想食自助餐"},{"pid":"3ad2c837f64819a205c57e135c40fef1805f2a68","tid":395820,"uid":20448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:19:53.000Z","msg":"搞手只求打個和<br />\n大家開開心心食返餐"},{"pid":"2d36db6a68484c2f0edf138e3b897ae90b1487b5","tid":395820,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:21:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自助餐係會比平時食多啲，但唔係要食返幾舊水返黎囉，人地做生意點都係計過有賺先做，食客身份係去享受，唔係同生意佬對賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n酒店來貨價係平，但係你自己都搵唔到邊度入貨可以咁平啦，最終咪又要食自助餐</blockquote><br />\n關咩事，自己煮好食好多，根本同食自助餐兩回事</blockquote><br />\n咁你講得出邊間買龍蝦同象拔蚌平咩??如果夠平嘅話,我以後唔食自助餐!!!!!!!</blockquote><br />\n波蝦唔做打手，去google打食材，網上訂購，好多間都平<br />\n象拔蚌大蚌一定貴，平既食細蚌，三十幾蚊隻，唔會差過大蚌。去大啲既街市水檔已經有得賣。</blockquote><br />\n象拔蚌依家都有得任食啦,食十隻已經回本</blockquote><br />\n都係嗰句，你無要求成日諗回本咪出去食自助餐。我就寧願享受優質食物，而唔係死食爛食。</blockquote><br />\n我就係試過,買爭鮮都係百幾蚊,但都係唔飽,仲要無我鐘意食嘅刺身,自助餐只係貴幾十,但乜都有得食"},{"pid":"c39a3a279245a7047efdc5944b88bee9319578c4","tid":395820,"uid":98680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:22:10.000Z","msg":"龍蝦幾十蚊斤<br />\n龍蝦係貴野<br />\n但真係唔係好貴囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係對比其他海鮮貴少少<br />\n更加唔洗講波龍同d凍肉貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你食到成本價5成你都偷笑啦"},{"pid":"56bda96eefd2780f8c5b022cd49a82e717c77dc8","tid":395820,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:28:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>龍蝦幾十蚊斤<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">龍蝦係貴野<br />\n但真係唔係好貴囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n只係對比其他海鮮貴少少<br />\n更加唔洗講波龍同d凍肉貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你食到成本價5成你都偷笑啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁矛盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5183b9975f2c7e265e20a543e33c61c93ca1cbc3","tid":395820,"uid":61832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:28:06.000Z","msg":"廣告撚？"},{"pid":"4f59039ac056d945ce451eaa7ed785062a57ac0c","tid":395820,"uid":28113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:30:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">邊度買平象拔蚌同龍蝦???如果夠平嘅話,我以後唔食自助餐!!!!!!!</span></blockquote><br />\n酒店可以用平咁多嘅價錢攞咩龍蝦、象拔蚌<br />\n我諗作為一個人都應該知佢攞貨係俾批發價<br />\n唔係買2、3隻龍蝦，要買一定數量<br />\n而酒店自助餐啲龍蝦，去貨量大，酒店自然攞更大量嘅貨<br />\n佢攞得咁大數量，肯定會同批發商要求更平嘅批發價<br />\n<br />\n就算你一日三餐，每餐食十隻龍蝦<br />\n個數量恐怕你一個月都食唔晒<br />\n前提係你有雪房，都唔擔保啲龍蝦擺一個月都唔變壞"},{"pid":"7a27b1296b53814a107d969975058cfa3365910a","tid":395820,"uid":6636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:47:52.000Z","msg":"以前開bbq店 可以答你最平嘅龍蝦10蚊都唔洗有大大隻"},{"pid":"8676d3a989d7ec8c98c804d59529f4fad9356de6","tid":395820,"uid":5777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:53:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/11/181006_882c821a797b08fadc927da2af346334.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F11%2F181006_882c821a797b08fadc927da2af346334.jpg&h=44d97011&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n龍蝦鮑魚帶子刺身全部任食我都唔知佢點賺<br />\n<br />\n仲有鴨肝片皮鴨HD雪糕</blockquote><br />\n邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c5a7e84d480e0953509d6f5afa7248d6672a418","tid":395820,"uid":44210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:58:43.000Z","msg":"條仆街一定係打手 switch個post係咁屌人買炒價 睇死佢係某公司打手"},{"pid":"751ec751c97df4b13bb11cad8988ac5ea07ea9c8","tid":395820,"uid":11703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:59:38.000Z","msg":"第一轉就新鮮<br />\n第二轉補充嗰啲已經冇咩鮮味，明顯雪咗一段時間"},{"pid":"08ccc8e6548555e89ac5f55e5d685a3af3aa99e8","tid":395820,"uid":81756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T11:03:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地餐廳批發入貨可能圍到10蚊隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該難d 美國當造超市都要40蚊左右一隻 當時間/"},{"pid":"eb33a7f9a0b2c82528f6e631e6fccf05d2fb6486","tid":395820,"uid":81756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T11:04:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>人地餐廳批發入貨可能圍到10蚊隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該難d 美國當造超市都要40蚊左右一隻 當時間/</blockquote><br />\n煮埋應該15蚊左右"},{"pid":"dadca957f605cf48766347931210f66cc82b7275","tid":395820,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T11:06:58.000Z","msg":"食自助餐過下引架姐 話要食回本真係傻鳩黎 比錢玩自己"},{"pid":"a2843b6aa2c83e415bb2cf60ba74b6e3d665aacc","tid":395820,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T11:07:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" cla