ass=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用自助餐價錢，我寧願出去單點</blockquote><br />\n單點計翻可能仲貴過buffet</blockquote><br />\n睇你食質素定係份量。<br />\n自助餐我最多食四轉。我諗$700出去食好野夠有突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n差唔多<br />\n一轉湯加沙律，兩轉主食，食兩件cake<br />\n七百蚊出去食靚好多。"},{"pid":"ea0c5a59b269c1cfcc739f36f2a8f619e7af36f1","tid":395820,"uid":561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T12:04:21.000Z","msg":"澳門君悅有新鮮游水龍蝦任食<br />\n500幾啦"},{"pid":"a1afd4e6cddbeb8b178f5b6ea927dca397ef9478","tid":395820,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T12:07:58.000Z","msg":"食任食要食到所謂回本真係好寒酸"}]}